      <label for ="q1c">C) Streaming</label><br>
      
     </div>


     <div class="form-group">
      <label>2) How important is speed to you?</label>
      <br>
        <input type="radio" id="q2yes" name="q2" value="a">
        <label for ="q2yes">Very Important</label><br>
        <input type="radio" id="q2no" name="q2" value="b">
        <label for="q2no">Not Important</label><br>
      
     </div>


     <div class="form-group">
        <label>3) Would you like to encrypt your data in a set block at a time or one bit at a time?</label>
        <br>
          <input type="radio" id="q3a" name="q3" value="a">
          <label for ="q3a">A) Block</label><br>
          <input type="radio" id="q3b" name="q3" value="b">
          <label for="q3b">B) One Bit </label><br>
        
    
       </div>

       <div class="form-group">
        <label>4) How important is security to you?</label>
        <br>
          <input type="radio" id="q4a" name="q4" value="a">
          <label for ="q4a">A) Very Important</label><br>
          <input type="radio" id="q4b" name="q4" value="b">
          <label for="q4b">B) Not Important</label><br>
        
       </div>

       



     <div class="form-group">
        <label> 5) In the data structure of your product, do you need to access data randomly?</label>
        <br>
          <input type="radio" id="q5a" name="q5" value="a">
          <label for ="q5a">A) Yes</label><br>
          <input type="radio" id="q5b" name="q5" value="b">
          <label for="q5b">B) No</label><br>
        
          
       </div>


     <div class="form-group" align="center">
      <input id="clickMe" type="submit" class="btn btn-info"  />
